Title: Bingo with The Elderly @Ren Ci Community Hospital
address: Ren Ci Community Hospital  71 Irrawaddy Road Singapore 329562
description: Ren Ci Community Hospital is a charity healthcare organisation committed to providing high quality and affordable medical care for the needy sick  based on the principles of loving kindness and compassion. We hope to recruit volunteers to play Bingo with our wheelchair-bound residents. Volunteers will spend time interacting and befriending our elderly. Bingo session will be held at wards 11  12 and 13. Each floor will have a separate Bingo session and music performance.
